# Web App Patterns

## Component Structure

- Use shadcn/ui components from `@/components/ui/`
- Custom components in `@/components/`
- Utility function: `cn()` from `@/lib/utils`
- Use Server Components by default; add `'use client'` only when needed

## State Management

- Zustand stores in `@/stores/`
- Engine types imported from `@viridian/engine/types`

```typescript
import { create } from 'zustand';
import type { Team, Player } from '@viridian/engine/types';
```

## Styling

- Tailwind CSS 4 utility classes
- Dark mode support (use `dark:` variant)
- Responsive: mobile-first with `sm:`, `md:`, `lg:` breakpoints

## Progressive Disclosure

- Summary first, drill-down on demand
- Contextual help tooltips on every complex concept
- Every major system reachable in 1 click from dashboard

## Delegation UI

Every management subsystem must offer manual / review / auto modes. Show delegation controls prominently so players can choose their engagement level.
